entries.npc_9: Great.  I'll take that, and you can go on in.
entries.player_8: I'm not ready to give it up yet.
entries.npc_6: I need somebody to go to Coronet and get something back from the CorSec properties.  A bowl of Borvo's that was stolen.  It's an antique.
entries.npc_5: Cause without going through me, you don't get to see Borvo.
entries.npc_4: Corellia.  Try the CorSec offices in Coronet.  I think he got busted.  It's probably in their property stash there.
entries.player_4: Why don't I just give it to Borvo?
entries.npc_3: Yeah, he'll send you back over.  Like you pointed out, he's MY buddy.
entries.npc_2: Borvo needs to get his antique bowl back.  One of our ex-partners took it and took off.  You get it back, give it to me, I'll let you in.
entries.player_2: Maybe I'll try your buddy there.
entries.npc_1: Can't let you in.  Not unless you're willing to do me a favor.
